Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.27,0:01:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多久沒像這樣兩個人一起喝酒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.63,0:01:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.10,0:01:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經這麼久了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.38,0:01:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就兩個月而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.63,0:01:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對叛徒的處置呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.73,0:01:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.21,0:01:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.57,0:02:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過看起來還不能完事的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.59,0:02:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用公眾輿論施壓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.41,0:02:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的後台應該是有相當地位的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.05,0:02:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能會是"Family"裡面的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.15,0:02:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛是不可饒恕的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.93,0:02:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.83,0:02:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因果報應啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為Millennion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為Millennion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.45,0:02:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.36,0:02:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 正在秘密調查的利古蘭德小組有報告進來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但好幾次想要聯絡他們卻都沒有回復
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:02:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 說來聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.80,0:02:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.89,0:03:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈利·麥克道韋爾名下美術品的進出口公司
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒店 保險金融投資公司 相關企業的經營
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.32,0:03:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有這些的營業總額是七千萬尤爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而收益就有兩千三百萬尤爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.44,0:03:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上交給"Family"的錢有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六百萬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年就有一千七百萬花花綠綠的鈔票流入哈利的腰包嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 哈利申報的是七百萬的收入
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他私吞的金額就是一千萬尤爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能把艾蘭克的酒店全都收購的資金
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這筆錢的去向呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.97,0:03:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 但這麼天衣無縫地隱瞞了錢的去向
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以確認哈里·麥克道韋爾作出了何等周密的佈置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.77,0:03:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴利古蘭德他們要多加注意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.97,0:03:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈利知道我們這邊的動向
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也知道我們還沒有能向Big Daddy報告的確鑿證據
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屬下明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈利·麥克道韋爾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種小混混居然有這樣的能耐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.45,0:04:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙很精明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.32,0:04:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為自己沒看錯他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.80,0:04:43.76,p,,0000,0000,0000,banner;10;0;50,本片字幕僅供試看，請於下載後二十四小時內刪除，禁止將本片用於任何商業行為，若因私自散佈造成法律問題，本論壇及字幕組概不負責！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙精明過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝 雪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 在發什麼呆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 真是好棒的房子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 花了不少錢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.62,0:04:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓將來和我一起生活的人覺得不自由啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.44,0:04:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人很幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是絕世美女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝爾·沃肯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,0:05:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說你買了房子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為來到這附近所以順便來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.57,0:05:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 歡迎歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是順便 而是專程過來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.41,0:05:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯再追加一人份
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否賞臉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.61,0:05:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九月之花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永不凋謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.26,0:05:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利古蘭德大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把東西交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是好不容易才到手的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:05:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Family"的命令是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.45,0:06:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那給我一塊地盤的事也是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.58,0:06:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.34,0:06:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼…呀 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩姆 你跟這個男人在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟蘭迪的情報負責人利古蘭德一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.23,0:06:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.96,0:06:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙說是"Family"的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.19,0:06:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所…所以… 大哥 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.72,0:06:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩姆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.35,0:06:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.88,0:06:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.57,0:06:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩姆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:07:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這四年來你在我們手下工作得很賣力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 若不夠心狠手辣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不能跟追隨那個男人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大 差不多該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.34,0:07:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布蘭登
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.88,0:07:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布蘭登
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.86,0:07:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老媽去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.05,0:07:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了你 老媽才能去住院
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後也沒有什麼痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也總算能理解我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這不孝子也算裝得挺孝順的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.32,0:08:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 不聯繫…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.10,0:08:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我這種可以扔到一邊的小雜碎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能勞煩組織的大幹部呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的世界是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 組織只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.93,0:08:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉來遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.64,0:08:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big…Daddy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威基·巴恩斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願令堂能在天國安息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.59,0:08:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你…Big Daddy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.19,0:09:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你所說的啊 布蘭登
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.41,0:09:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 布蘭登
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然拜託你來當保鏢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,0:09:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不敢當
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.71,0:09:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫瓦倫蒂那的客人要到法萊斯特朗皇室去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是否在打什麼壞主意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.51,0:09:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要靠你的雙眼來確認
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.34,0:09:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:10:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得怎麼樣 這是為您定制的菜單
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.57,0:10:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不勝感激
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.69,0:10:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你到這裡來想幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.78,0:10:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會只是想吃頓飯而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先迴避一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.89,0:10:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常滿意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.28,0:10:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單刀直入地說 哈利·麥克道韋爾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是要成為Millennion的老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.59,0:10:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和搭檔的布蘭登·西特一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,0:10:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊請
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:11:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑我一個人的力量\N就連為偉大的Big Daddy提鞋的機會也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 有布蘭登·西特在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他在一起的話 我就能升到任何位置
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.91,0:11:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這樣堅信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越往上爬就會越困難
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.51,0:11:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喪命的可能性也越大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得不作出決斷的事情也多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.62,0:11:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是個脆弱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.59,0:11:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 想要變強
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要像令嬡那樣支持我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.49,0:11:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝爾·沃肯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.08,0:11:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所相信的不是你的言詞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是我這雙眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈利·麥克道韋爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小女就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.45,0:12:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想見你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.12,0:12:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布蘭登
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.91,0:12:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和哈利關係還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有吵架嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.18,0:12:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒干危險的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.78,0:12:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.68,0:13:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 這樣就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.86,0:13:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是它 你送的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,適合我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.85,0:13:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.07,0:13:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 再好好看看我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.49,0:13:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想更瞭解布蘭登
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.11,0:13:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 講我聽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都行 只要是你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.98,0:13:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼好說的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.29,0:14:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.99,0:14:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布蘭登
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.44,0:14:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…我對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.29,0:14:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布蘭登
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 這把年紀還做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.67,0:15:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy對瑪麗亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個老頭子對年輕的女孩又能如何…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘲笑我也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.43,0:15:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.45,0:15:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能加入Millennion太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.31,0:15:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 打心底這麼覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到她那裡去吧 到瑪麗亞身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為人上之人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.37,0:16:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈利 爸爸說今天就留在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.88,0:16:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…別離開我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.45,0:16:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.26,0:16:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.74,0:16:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇往直前吧 布蘭登
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.64,0:16:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 我們兩個一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了我的野心和自由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了Millennion
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利古蘭德那裡的聯繫中斷了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.29,0:17:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.86,0:17:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.93,0:17:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一件怪事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的秘密賬戶上多了一千萬尤爾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且來源不明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.13,0:17:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆 前面的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 蘭迪非常懷疑哈利的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.44,0:17:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他連哈利·麥克道韋爾的計劃一點都不…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊已經把錢轉到蘭迪那邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是由誰去幹掉蘭迪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是手法不夠高明的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝爾·沃肯的Overkills就可能會出來管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:17:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經準備了一個勝任的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.53,0:18:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有比他更合適的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.33,0:18:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九頭文治
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的確沒有背叛組織
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.56,0:18:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你背叛了哈利·麥克道韋爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.05,0:18:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.75,0:18:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭迪…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.30,0:19:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我推薦進組織的就是那位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.06,0:19:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從頭教給我組織的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.88,0:19:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能晉陞得這麼快 都多虧了那位在"Family"面前的美言
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.55,0:19:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 Millennion和"Family"有著鐵一般的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.76,0:19:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能賦予背叛者的只有…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死 而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.38,0:19:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他背叛的原因嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.57,0:19:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到現在還不能相信蘭迪會背叛組織
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.49,0:19:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他對Daddy比我還要忠心耿耿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.78,0:20:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.24,0:20:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女兒托付給了你 所以我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈利·麥克道韋爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.50,0:20:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定不負所望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.95,0:20:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布蘭登呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.29,0:20:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在善後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.22,0:20:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布蘭登·西特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.45,0:20:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.11,0:20:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛是不可饒恕的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.89,0:20:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊都清理好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.83,0:21:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.38,0:21:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.21,0:21:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.61,0:21:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.26,0:21:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了一直承受這種痛苦而建立組織
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.12,0:21:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並活到現在的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.63,0:21:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭迪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.13,0:21:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.24,0:21:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.58,0:21:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.21,0:21:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓我一個人呆一會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.13,0:21:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.39,0:21:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.88,0:22:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.51,0:22:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不準備晚飯的話 等蘭迪回來就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.53,0:22:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會抱怨的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.06,0:22:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點 伯母
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.19,0:22:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會背叛的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.14,0:22:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.55,0:24:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.35,0:24:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經一起開懷大笑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.93,0:24:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.69,0:24:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經發誓一起勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.43,0:24:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈利·麥克道韋爾
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.19,0:24:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你…
